cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.IT, cs.LG 

The paper deals with video super resolution, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of motion information and optimization techniques suggests that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of regularization and parameter balancing suggests that the paper could also belong to the sub-categories of information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG).
